}}'''Kazakhstan''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in December 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Astana (Nur-Sultan), along with Almaty and Shymkent.

On December 19, 2019 on iOS; new countries were added. Along with Kazakhstan; there was also Austria, Bahamas, Costa Rica, DR Congo, Kenya, Kuwait, Lebanon, Mongolia, Nepal, Ukraine, and Vietnam. This was added in the ''Friends'' Update.

==Information==
Characters graduate at 17 and can legally drive at 18.

